        <h2>About Stray Kids</h2>
        <p class="about">Stray Kids is a K-Pop boygroup created through the survival show "Stray Kids" created by JYP entertainment. They debuted as 9 on March 25th, 2018. They remain as 8 today, one of the members having left in 2019. They are often known for their unique sound, shocking certain fans due to the vast difference from typical K-Pop.</p>
        <img class="centre1" src="Stray Kids 0801 planes.jpg" alt="All Stray Kids members facing away while throwing paper planes in their 0801 MV" width="300px" height="170px">
        <p class="about">They are a self-produced group, creating and producing all their songs on their own, primarily written by 3RACHA (Bangchan, Changbin, and HAN). The group has done tours in most continents, and are hoping to be able to see STAYs all around the world! STAY is their fan name, and they have a little mascot created in early 2026 for their fans.</p>
        <img class="centre1" src="STAY.jpg" alt="mascot of STAY" height="175" width="150">
        <br><br>
        <p class="about">This isn't some official site, I just made this for fun! Though I am updating it often as I can!</p>
